Package GUI

This package contain Graphical implement classes of the game.
Since:
0.20
Version:
0.30
Author:
Bach Vu, Linh Luu
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CrewPanel
    This class make instances of JPanel, which is used to create 4 instances (for each crew) in the pause frame, Crew tab.
    GameEnvironment
    This is the third frame, player actually start their game.
    LoadingFrame  
    MissionFrame
    This is the second frame, if player choose new game.
    OutpostTrade
    This is the trade frame, if player's spaceship get close to one of the outpost and interact (X).
    PauseFrame
    This is the pause frame, if player press ESC at anytime.
    ScanPlanetFrame  
    SpaceshipController
    This class make instances of JPanel, which Game Environment can initiate multiple galaxies.
    WelcomeFrame
    Class Intro: This is the First and Begin Frame, player choose New game, Load game or view Credits.
